import React from 'react'
import styled from 'styled-components'
import SEction  from './SEction'

function Home() {
  return (
    <Container>
        <SEction
        title= "Model S"
        />
        <SEction
        title="Mosel X"
        />
        <SEction
        title="Model Y"
        />
        <SEction
        title="Model 3"
        />
    </Container>
  )
}


export default Home

const Container = styled.div`
  height: 100vh;  
`
